@startuml
title Модель состояний процесса государственного аудита
header Диаграмма состояний (State Machine)
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> New : new FinancialReport()

state "Регистрация отчета" as New
New : Status = New

New --> StaffActive : RunAudit() / TakeDuty()

state "Персонал на смене" as StaffActive
StaffActive : Inspector/Auditor -> Idle

StaffActive --> SystemReady : VerificationSystem.Start()

state "Система готова" as SystemReady
SystemReady : System -> Operational

SystemReady --> Scanning : Цикл по отчетам

state "Проверка данных" as Scanning
Scanning : system.PerformScan()

Scanning --> Verified : [Sum < Limit] / Verify()
Scanning --> AuditFailed : [Sum >= Limit] (Превышение лимита)

state "Отчет верифицирован" as Verified
Verified : Report -> Verified

Verified --> ProtocolValid : Auditor.SignProtocol()
Verified --> AuditFailed : [RequestCount > 100] (Сбой системы)
Verified --> AuditFailed : [Auditor == OffDuty] (Ошибка полномочий)

state "Протокол сформирован" as ProtocolValid
ProtocolValid : Protocol -> Valid

ProtocolValid --> EntryReady : DigitalRegistry.Prepare()
ProtocolValid --> AuditFailed : [Report == Corrupted] (Ошибочный формат)
ProtocolValid --> AuditFailed : [Registry == Full] (Реестр переполнен)

state "Запись подготовлена" as EntryReady
EntryReady : Entry -> Ready

EntryReady --> Committed : Registry.AddEntry()

state "Данные внесены" as Committed
Committed : Entry -> Committed\nController -> Syncing

Committed --> Archived : report.MarkAsArchived()

state "Отчет архивирован" as Archived
Archived : Report -> Archived

Archived --> Scanning : [Есть еще отчеты]
Archived --> Completed : [Все отчеты обработаны]

state "Аудит завершен успешно" as Completed
Completed : Audit -> Completed

state "Аудит провален" as AuditFailed
AuditFailed : Audit -> Failed

Completed --> [*]
AuditFailed --> [*]
@enduml